    "7406603": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Monglane",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "The registration counter at the front desk... This is it! Let's try our luck!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hello, Ms. Monglane!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Monglane",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "(Whoa! She doesn't look like she's easy to get along with!)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(Maybe the Art of Negotiation will work?)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "(That's right, we've got this book! Who knew it would come in handy here?)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Let's see... Found it! \"If you gain the initiative by showing your strength and overwhelm your opponent with an imposing manner...\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "This is it! Overwhelm the opponent by being imposing! Paimon gets it! Paimon just has to be louder, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey! Ms. Monglane! Hello—"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Monglane",
                    "T": "...I heard you. What I can do for you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? It really worked!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Hehe, we're here for the satisfaction survey, Ms. Monglane! Er, Paimon means to say that she's here to accompany {M#him}{F#her}."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#(Don't worry, {NICKNAME}. We have this book. Paimon will sneak peeks at the book and tell you what to do! Anyway... Yeah! Just listen to Paimon!)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Monglane",
                    "T": "Another one saw the notes in the books..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? Yeah, that's right!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Monglane",
                    "T": "Just how many were...? Actually... Ugh, forget it. It's fine..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Monglane",
                    "T": "Ahem, please wait a moment... Allow me to explain the rules. The survey has a total of five questions. Please answer them quickly and intuitively. Remember, you must answer them quickly."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Monglane",
                    "T": "Do you understand? We can begin once you're ready."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
